3. cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) - The paper deals with power control for nodes, which is a common topic in networking and internet architecture. 
4. cs.MA (Multiagent Systems) - The paper proposes a policy for a system with multiple agents (energy harvesting nodes), which falls under the scope of multiagent systems.
